    ek model bana deta hai 
    ye defined hota hai ki kya kya hoga 
    push pop pull operations agar perform krne ho to agar alag alag array pe work krenge to complex hoga isliye class banayi ki same array pe kam kro

init function = constructor 
    class ke andar koi bhi ek chij ho jo everytime jitne functions honge usme access krni hi krni hai to use constructor bana do
    jaise hi class ka object banega to ye constructor apne aap call ho jayega if it's useful for you then use it else not...
    oops code made the code efficient 
    now stackADT me self khud call ho jayega
    
self.data 
    self me ab data dal dia 
    list dal dia 
    yani list ko constructor bana dia 
    ab jab class ka object banega to ye function apne aap call ho jayega
    self ek object hai jisme data stored hai 

push function   
    push function me self,x ko btane ki jrurat ni pdegi 
    ye khud self.data ko utha lega

pop function
    same ye self.data se khud data ko utha lega cause it is a constructor
    ye pehle check krega kya list me kuch data hai bhi ya nhi
    agar data nhi hua to none 
    agar data hua to nikal dega

is empty
    wha function ko call kr rhe the yha data ko def krdia 

